'Nobody has been arrested at this stage - officers will be speaking to a man concerning the matter.'

Revealing the cannabis find on their Twitter page, Tipton Green Neighbourhood Policing Team said: 'Shame this establishment didn’t heed it’s (sic) own sign huh..? Licensee to be dealt with..watch this space!'

A picture taken inside the ladies’ toilet shows an officer surrounded by the green plants with the sink barely visible.

It also appears that the drugs are being hidden by boards on a shelf above the toilets.

The pub is currently closed.

